caption.text:
Facing Daily Problems ••• Since highschool, my fanboy-ing life is almost all about Tame Impala. That was Innerspeaker and Lonerism era. Then suddenly Currents appeared, my all-time favorite records become trio.  Currents is a bunch of melancholic poems wrapped in an awesome groove. It is melancholic yet dance-able. Parker talks about sadness and daily problems in a dance-able way. That's what makes Currents my favorite. The songs are always on my playlist. 
People may have different interpretations about Currents, but I do believe they have the same direction for listening to Currents. To walk away from sadness and face the problems. Cheers 😬😁 #ganaraxmonkaxkiosplay #makeitfun #tameimpalajkt #covercontest @ganaraartspace @kiosplay @monkamagicstore
